AddFancyLighting: One or more biomes in Origins is best experienced with the mod "Fancy Lighting"
FerventArms: Fervent Arms removes some content from Terraria Origins
RetroBad: The "Retro" and "Trippy" lighting modes disable many visual effects, and some visual effects may not be always disabled completely, leading to stability issues
ClearAll: Right click to ignore all suggestions
ToManyItems: Some npcs may run out of space in their shops so it would be best to have Shop Extender to be able to buy every item from each npc
ToManyItemsAlch: Some npcs may run out of space in their shops, especially so with AlchemistNPC so it would be best to have Shop Extender to be able to buy every item from each npc
